{"tid":1698933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【區選】國家隊𠝹票","createTime":"2019-11-08T00:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:04:27.000Z","uid":61520,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"549054e06a7f9c6af671a57fc8fc5365ed9e70d4","tid":1698933,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"睇咗有位手足post 咗油尖旺有大陸仔𠝹票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696646/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696646/page/1</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗你老味𠝹票撚肯定唔只一件<br />\n果然發現自己嗰區同附近有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國家隊</span></strong>出來𠝹票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係小弟嘅 findings, 幫助大家判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟發現有8條柒頭好可能係國家隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃惠達</span></strong> (E05<span style=\"color: blue;\">油尖旺-富榮</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡其隆</span></strong> (E12 <span style=\"color: blue;\">油尖旺-大南</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉智豪</span></strong> (F02 <span style=\"color: blue;\">深水埗-長沙灣</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">王曉聖</span></strong> (F03<span style=\"color: blue;\">深水埗-南昌北</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林浩楠</span></strong> (F21<span style=\"color: blue;\">深水埗-李鄭屋</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林天恩</span></strong> (G01<span style=\"color: blue;\">九龍城-馬頭</span>圍)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李浩培</span></strong> (G18<span style=\"color: blue;\">九龍城-鶴園海逸</span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李進龍</span></strong> (G23<span style=\"color: blue;\">九龍城-家維</span>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuaxoie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyuaxoie.jpg&h=096d6246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班死撚樣有以下共通點:<br />\n- 全部係柒頭<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">武警公安撚樣</span></span>, 資料又唔齊, 冇忽似香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 全鳩部提名日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後嗰日先報名</span></span>, 明顯係𠝹票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 全部候選人簡介係用 PowerPoint template 做, 有冇咁啱先? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">===============================================</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃惠達</span> </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(E05油尖旺-富榮): <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選油尖旺係都講831喇,</span> 做乜講元朗721?  唔通本來assign 落元朗? <br />\n同區有民主黨 李偉峰 &amp; 民建聯 鍾港武<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oD1Ak7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoD1Ak7f.jpg&h=1f5a33de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡其隆</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(E12 油尖旺-大南): 根本係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>武警公安</strong></span>柒頭, 成條撚樣, 仲要填嘅名同banner 名唔match, 你係Choi Ki Lung 定 Choi Keng Lung ? 媽, 我好亂<br />\n同區有 社區前進 李國權&amp; 經民聯 李思敏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20wpesA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20wpesA.jpg&h=ad581131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉智豪</span></strong> (F02 深水埗-長沙灣): PowerPoint 撻字style, 字體顏色好難睇, 專業少少好唔好? 個樣明明係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>送水佬</strong></span>, 點撚解要扮文員仔? <br />\n同區有長沙灣社區發展力量 李文浩 &amp; 經民聯 龐朝輝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iqtF7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iqtF7K.jpg&h=1840d641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">王曉聖</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (F03深水埗-南昌北): <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫民賤聯鄭泳舜助攻</span></strong>, 十惡補不赦, 同區有公民黨 劉家衡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7w7G07X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7w7G07X.jpg&h=678034c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面仲有"},{"pid":"9be2b13ff97bb56c224137d802f4af3373199f53","tid":1698933,"uid":61520,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林浩楠</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (F21深水埗-李鄭屋): PowerPoint 又係撻字style, 字體顏色好難睇, 似十足葉智豪個 banner style , <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">外賣仔look 扮建造業</span></strong>, 專業少少好唔好?<br />\n同區有經民聯 陳鏡秋 &amp; 民協 江貴生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ON9qJms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FON9qJms.jpg&h=b5bf8c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林天恩</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (G01九龍城-馬頭圍) : 這是正式取錄的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武警</span></strong>嗎? 負責駕駛軍車的司機嗎? 條撚樣gel 咗頭都洗唔走武警味囉<br />\n同區有 獨立 曾健超 &amp; 民建聯 邵天虹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbp6sOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frbp6sOg.jpg&h=12fef761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李浩培</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(G18九龍城-鶴園海逸): 這是正式取錄的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武警</span></strong>嗎? 負責批發武器嗎? 你以為叫自己做Patrick 就無人知你係國家隊? Banner 內容抄林天恩, 專業少少好唔好?<br />\n同區有 民主黨 郭天立 &amp; 自稱獨立余志榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6f9qz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6f9qz9.jpg&h=75d2c4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李進龍</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(G23九龍城-家維): <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大陸柒味</span></strong>濃到爆炸, 同蔡其隆都係自稱做物流 (順X快遞?), 不論Banner 同件 Polo  嘅 style 都好撚似, 根本係一夥<br />\n同區有 民主黨 周熙雯 &amp; 自稱獨立  勞超傑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LyySfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LyySfk.jpg&h=26516891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老味, Zoom 埋張車頭相睇, 發現<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">蔡其隆, 王曉聖, 林天恩,李進龍</span></span></strong>個眼神光係一鳩樣! 問過識影相嘅 friend, 佢話四個柒頭個眼光一定係同一燈光setting 先打到出來, 四個自稱無 &ldquo;政治聯繫&rdquo;, 去同一個studio影相, 有無咁啱阿?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trbwDVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrbwDVu.jpg&h=1d0cf47c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國家隊出來𠝹票係預咗, 齋係九龍我都搵到8件武警, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各位手足睇路</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>驅逐共狗 光復香港  時代革命</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2a153ba98ed9f873fe3ac087c3ef4040cc37b1","tid":1698933,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:19:20.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n【區選】國家隊𠝹票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afcf0d10838bad2102002a277d07f276e9480c5b","tid":1698933,"uid":39682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:23:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba645cb87a3c012501f4814118a26463005bbf0d","tid":1698933,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574b976ce203be4a9a506191ff0f619cb0313b0f","tid":1698933,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92e2893a39a6f5393db6041d4790b63bbfb215bb","tid":1698933,"uid":120658,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"又好似幾有道理wo<br />\n寧願投白票都唔好投錯票"},{"pid":"e8facb60a4d5bd9957a894522d9bcdbced3c1e7d","tid":1698933,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2115f089904b8ab0925544a12d2cdb355fb79d","tid":1698933,"uid":240971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fbea9569ff2631afd4200f03ceed18cfcc704e","tid":1698933,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e2893a39a6f5393db6041d4790b63bbfb215bb","tid":1698933,"uid":120658,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"又